ee also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert d’Apleby was born about 1170, in Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Mrs. Robert d Apleby. He died about 1225, in his hometown, at the age of 57."},"et":{"about 1170–about 1225":"umbes 1170–umbes 1225","1171–Female":"1171–Surnud","1196–1248":"1196–1248","1170–1225":"1170–1225","about 1170":"umbes 1170","1248":"1248","1225":"1225","about 1225":"umbes 1225","1196":"1196","1171":"1171","about 1196":"umbes 1196","1170":"1170","Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Buglawton, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1170–about 1225":"noin 1170–noin 1225","1171–Female":"1171–Kuollut","1196–1248":"1196–1248","1170–1225":"1170–1225","about 1170":"noin 1170","1248":"1248","1225":"1225","about 1225":"noin 1225","1196":"1196","1171":"1171","about 1196":"noin 1196","1170":"1170","Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Buglawton, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1170–about 1225":"environ 1170–environ 1225","1171–Female":"1171–Décédée","1196–1248":"1196–1248","1170–1225":"1170–1225","about 1170":"environ 1170","1248":"1248","1225":"1225","about 1225":"environ 1225","1196":"1196","1171":"1171","about 1196":"environ 1196","1170":"1170","Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Buglawton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert d’Apleby est né environ 1170, à Buglawton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Mrs. Robert d Apleby. Il est décédé environ 1225, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 57 ans."},"de":{"about 1170–about 1225":"um 1170–um 1225","1171–Female":"1171–Verstorben","1196–1248":"1196–1248","1170–1225":"1170–1225","about 1170":"um 1170","1248":"1248","1225":"1225","about 1225":"um 1225","1196":"1196","1171":"1171","about 1196":"um 1196","1170":"1170","Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Buglawton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Robert d’Apleby